            <h6 class="border-bottom border-gray">About List-O-Rama (Business Service)</h6>
            <div class="col-md-9">
                <span class="text-semi">
                    List-O-Rama is a platform for :
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Individual consumers or a group of consumers</strong> to create and share lists for a common need or a specific purpose. Common uses are weekly shopping, party or event planning, to-do lists. etc.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Merchants </strong> to increase customer base, increase sales, and grow revenue. This is accomplished by offering incentives and discounts to existing clients, or targeting specific demographics or groups to increase customer base. Insight on Who buys, When they buy, Why they buy, What they buy, and How they buy, and how much they spend.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            The platform <strong>connects users with merchants </strong>for mutual benefits. Users get suggestions and discounts.  Merchants get customers and insights
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </span>
            </div>
            <h6 class="border-bottom border-gray">Key Points</h6>
            <div class="col-md-9">
                <span class="text-semi">
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>API Consumption</strong> : The app consumes NPS API for chart data. We couldn't find an API related to our app so used the NPS API instead.</li>
                        <li><strong>Usability + Look & Feel</strong> : Works well on devices of all size, small (mobile phones), medium (tablets) and big (desktops).We have used SVGs in place of images as they are lite weight and scale well easily across devices.Easy nvigation with large buttons and fewer clicks. Non verbose links have tooltips. The site runs same on all different browsers.</li>
                        <li><strong>Many-to-Many Relationships</strong> : Users and Lists, Users and Groups</li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>CRUD Operations</strong>:
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Create</strong> - User Signup, List Creation, Creation of Groups and Group Memebers</li>
                                <li><strong>Read</strong> - User Login, List Dashboard, Groups and Group Memebers display</li>
                                <li><strong>Update</strong> - Groups and Group Memebers updates</li>
                                <li><strong>Delete</strong> - Delete List items, Groups and Group memebers</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Chart</strong> : Doughnut chart using NPS API on Dashboard </svg> and Breakup of lits (Chart) <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10pt" height="10pt" class="svg-inline--fa fa-chart-pie fa-w-17" role="img" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 544 512" focusable="false"
